,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:43:39.000Z","msg":"推 要有獨立思考"},{"pid":"acecbeaa2b91a82ae9c363ae8a1a4c3d2616acb9","tid":1418382,"uid":98091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:45:07.000Z","msg":"推 講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679a0cbc744c4bf7923baedfaf07dd8f9a756353","tid":1418382,"uid":101057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:45:23.000Z","msg":"巴打頭腦好清晰！！推爆佢！！"},{"pid":"cc010d16dbcf618733baf0ed787926bee4351ccf","tid":1418382,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:45:46.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dwROzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dwROzT</a>"},{"pid":"92ca527573609f8f524892cea24c55ed0b770c7d","tid":1418382,"uid":128261,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:46:06.000Z","msg":"我代表勇武宣佈樓主係三毛"},{"pid":"2da387ac2f1f10a59cfd2806bad1967ddee879e2","tid":1418382,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40ac777d358c54ece5afffc9814f8c735f129286","tid":1418382,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"今日左膠累事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:46:20.000Z","msg":"但左膠不願面對"},{"pid":"ae0bb48a1f5e91968c47014fb525ce1d1d6447f9","tid":1418382,"uid":125219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:46:54.000Z","msg":"推呀呀"},{"pid":"ff0c4e4131963ebb11e646fb10ca0c5f6a2404c5","tid":1418382,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:47:06.000Z","msg":"0244 唔該所有人開突發post加個時間係前面<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pi